data.description: Lovely two story home is situated in Georgetown Meadows, Van Alstyne. Charming curb appeal with a two car garage and a front porch. Step inside to vaulted ceilings and Formal Living or Dining is off the entry way, this space could also make a perfect in home office! Sprawling Kitchen showcases stainless steel appliances, tiled backsplash, a raised breakfast bar plus an abundance of cabinets and counter space. Eat in Breakfast Nook! Full size utility! Large Living room showcases a cast stone fireplace and windows that overlook the backyard! Upstairs you will find a Huge Game Room, perfect for your pool table. Spacious Guest Bedrooms. The Primary Bedroom is very nicely sized and features an en-suite bath with dual sinks, linen cabinets, walk in closet, garden tub plus a separate shower! The backyard offers a covered patio and an expanded open patio. This is a great space to enjoy family BBQ's! Storage Shed plus a nicely sized yard to enjoy!  Enjoy the Pool and park at no extra cost!
